00:45:51.488 --> 00:45:53.083
If by solutions--
my argument is not

00:45:53.083 --> 00:45:54.750
whether technology
is a solution or not.

00:45:54.750 --> 00:45:57.960
My argument is whether it
is a sufficient solution.

00:45:57.960 --> 00:46:00.150
So I'll stick with
my soccer metaphor.

00:46:00.150 --> 00:46:02.940
I think player seven
can score, but she's not

00:46:02.940 --> 00:46:03.963
going to win by herself.

00:46:03.963 --> 00:46:05.880
She needs the other 10
players, and technology

00:46:05.880 --> 00:46:07.076
